    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mall Simulator 是一款轻松的第一人称模拟游戏，在这里你将体验经营一家拥有众多商店的巨大购物中心：</strong>  <br><br><strong>👕 服装 ⚽ 运动 💻 科技 🧸 玩具 🛒 超市 💄 化妆品  <br>🎬 电影院 🍔 汉堡店 🕹️ 游戏厅 🏠 家居用品 🎮 游戏商店  <br>🥐 面包店 💍 珠宝店 🌸 花店 🍣 寿司吧 🥤 自动售货机 💵 自动取款机</strong>  <br><br><strong>……在你的超级购物中心还有更多精彩等你探索！</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/982078ee35bc6d7359c45d948700ff02.avif?t=1772059192\" width=800 height=101 /></span>设计很重要！为你的购物中心打造最佳设计并管理你的商店。展示你的畅销店铺，为顾客打造完美的购物中心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/37eeae65d6b3464ec5efc16593df5b7b.poster.avif?t=1772059192\" width=748 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/37eeae65d6b3464ec5efc16593df5b7b.webm?t=1772059192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/37eeae65d6b3464ec5efc16593df5b7b.mp4?t=1772059192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/f817696ab744f7ac2d68bad695342d99.avif?t=1772059192\" width=800 height=101 /></span>从零到英雄！在你的购物中心开设最知名品牌的新店，销售他们的产品。从杂货店到珠宝店，不断扩展你的商店种类。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/55ddfd6444237d33b76b3d415003d410.poster.avif?t=1772059192\" width=748 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/55ddfd6444237d33b76b3d415003d410.webm?t=1772059192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/55ddfd6444237d33b76b3d415003d410.mp4?t=1772059192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/b5d24cd55cd6d6da37941599d5ca1d83.avif?t=1772059192\" width=800 height=101 /></span>缺货了？及时补充新产品，紧跟潮流，确保顾客留在你的购物中心。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/4c48eed1f6dfcb1bee595b64abbd9c0b.poster.avif?t=1772059192\" width=748 height=420 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/4c48eed1f6dfcb1bee595b64abbd9c0b.webm?t=1772059192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/4c48eed1f6dfcb1bee595b64abbd9c0b.mp4?t=1772059192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/0eae0ddea55ff8c574b00e3722235f5f.avif?t=1772059192\" width=800 height=101 /></span>时间就是金钱！你的购物中心可能会很繁忙，快速收款并雇用新员工，避免让顾客等待。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/50443e9f5c79e6ca22e7a85350f1c979.poster.avif?t=1772059192\" width=750 height=422 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/50443e9f5c79e6ca22e7a85350f1c979.webm?t=1772059192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/50443e9f5c79e6ca22e7a85350f1c979.mp4?t=1772059192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/b7d4bff74d65127ef091d5c1e5387c69.avif?t=1772059192\" width=800 height=101 /></span>打破墙壁！开辟新空间，为你的购物中心带来更多商店和品牌。 <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/bf17e6d5350077822e76a5fe2be47b82.poster.avif?t=1772059192\" width=744 height=418 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/bf17e6d5350077822e76a5fe2be47b82.webm?t=1772059192\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3180150/extras/bf17e6d5350077822e76a5fe2be47b82.mp4?t=1772059192\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>在《Mall Simulator》中，顾客满意度至关重要。你需要紧跟潮流，开设新店，设定合理的价格，并扩大购物中心，以避免破产。</strong></p>",
